highlights.text: Kendrick Lamar has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “HUMBLE.” is the highest at #4.
“That's What I Like” by Bruno Mars has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 21 weeks straight.
“Malibu” by Miley Cyrus is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #9.
“No Vacancy” by OneRepublic is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 98 spots at #102.
